After pouring through the incident reports and logs on the behavior of this SCP, the frightening possibility still persists: It may be able to escape any time it wants. The selection of victims is far from random, again showing signs of sentience. Our concerns are there could be outlet would-be-victims that the Foundation is not aware of at this time. Or there is an even darker possibility, there are outlets that it still has not chosen to use to escape.

